    "b The AgF was imaged with µ-CT to generate 3D models of the macroporous foam network.",
    "The average diameter of the pores is 262 µm, and the void space occupied 84.1% of the total volume of the material.",
    "c-e SEM images of the AgF@AgM structure at increasing magnification.",
    "The pore size distribution of the mesoporous Ag was estimated using SEM and had an average pore diameter of 28 ± 4 nm.",
